Key Match Events: Netherlands defeated Bangladesh by 87 runs as they dismissed all the Bangladeshi players for 142 runs.
Paul van Meekeren took 4 wickets for the Netherlands.
Bas de Leede picked 2 wickets for the Netherlands.
Colin Ackermann, Logan van Beek, and Aryan Dutt each took one wicket for the Netherlands.
Scott Edwards scored 68 runs for the Netherlands.
Wesley Barresi scored 41 runs for the Netherlands.
Shoriful Islam, Taskin Ahmed, Mustafizur Rahman, and Mahedi Hasan each took two wickets for Bangladesh.
Skipper Shakib Al Hasan picked one wicket for Bangladesh.
Mehidy Hasan Miraz scored 35 runs for Bangladesh.
Mustafizur Rahman scored 20 runs for Bangladesh.
Paul van Meekeren was named 'Player of the Match'.
